Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.10,Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\blur2\3c&HD1DBE1&}I cannot just watch over an invalid
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:27.39,Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\blur2\3c&HD1DBE1&}for the rest of my life…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:35.82,Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\blur2\3c&HD1DBE1&}Thanks to her…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.78,Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\blur2\3c&HD1DBE1&}I cannot do what I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.64,Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\blur2\3c&HD1DBE1&}Setsuko. Aah! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:15.19,Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\blur2\3c&HD1DBE1&}I will never be able to get ahead.
