Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where did all the other passengers go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it’s your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re all waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This train will never stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:14.43,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t care!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you’ll stay here—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:20.51,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:22.05,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,618,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}No! I won’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you can help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help Setsuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt so sorry that she’d been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him.{\alpha&HFF&} Show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him. Show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the cats doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories are tied to a single place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memory brings about Regret,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it is through Regret that fates intertwine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All is turned upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Form, Truth and Regret, all can be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you show me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the reason for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your Regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor Fukuda is corrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s hear what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this information reliable?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have it on good authority that\Nthe mayor is meeting with executives
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the railroad company on a regular basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there’s nothing illegal about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don’t you think it unlikely
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:48.93,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,626)}I’m sorry, Ichikawa, but we’re not a tabloid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they’re just making small talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not enough information for a proper article.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you’re just jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous of who{m}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re jealous of me, Moria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re jealous that I got such a huge story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not a story at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nothing to be jealous about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t publish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it was a mistake to send you into the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bit off more than you could chew.\NI’m putting you back on the advice column.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not giving up on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll get to the bottom of this. Mark my words!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:27.33,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get me wrong, Ichikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you’re a great—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo, yeah! Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman peeping at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let them beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeed, I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this still not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry for being so hard on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Ichikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right! I knew she had it in her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I was so hard on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you developed the shots yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the film?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let’s go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a huge scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t let afford to let anyone know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even one of our co-workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here’s the mayor with Touto Railways’ Board of Directors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he is with Nohinbashi Construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They met at Kisshou Hotel in Kajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mayor recently passed a city\Nordinance at the rail company’s request.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he received a considerable bribe in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does he bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ichi’i Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mayor’s uncle is its president.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more than enough information to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is front page material.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have it on my desk tomorrow\Nnight. We’ll run it the next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not much time, but can you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to write the whole article?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did all the work, so you should reap the benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I misjudged you, Moria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure you thought of me as a weak, worthless woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that only a man could become a real reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn’t be more wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m finally a real newswoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where Hichiriki Zaka’s Konata Inn is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Write it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prevent any leaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t let anyone know about this article.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll put it on the page myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the very same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Actually, I have a proposition for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it’s not very pleasant at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason to meet anywhere else, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Regret{\alpha&HFF} is close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Regret is close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promise to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I’m begging you. I want to be famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t stand to rot away here the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the man I spoke to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually had fun last night, for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Konata Inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a telephone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m different from that loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a newswoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ichikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People have asked me if I wanted to be a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re sure you weren’t followed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong, Moria-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look so afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, poppycock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not as though we’ll be killed or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just went to see if she was all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s the article?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to read it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.88,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,626)}I can’t let this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just following orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masao!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masao, are you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria-san, you can’t do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll tell our superiors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No use. I’ve already spoken to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I’m not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You planned this from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were always going to steal my—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:42.17,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,626)}I’m sorry. I had to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward! You snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You planned it from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll talk her out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll tell the Chief Editor! I’ll get you fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:14:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be quite a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it’s not really my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:04.78,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I’ll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.24,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:11.78,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Damn you! Damn you! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I’m jealous of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn’t do this over such petty concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:17.16,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Damn you! Damn you! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a woman to the end, never\Nable to catch on when it really counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching her from a much higher position.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not hesitate in executing this order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t have this turning into a scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re working for Mayor Fukuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you? How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:42.85,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you women are so blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no ability to read a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:44.78,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never wanted to{\alpha&HFF&} print the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never wanted to print the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll take orders from me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll have it printed somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have the proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve fooled you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll never give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only time I really feel alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people won’t allow this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old hag…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish she would just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a stupid woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you fair warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.09,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Made me kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.35,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,619,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}Made me kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman reporter bit off more than she could chew,\Nand committed suicide after having her dreams shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts. It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No, it can’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, notice me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t hit me! You have to notice me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s not even good enough for the back page.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here’s your payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is a suicide. A suicide, I’m sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll never{\alpha&HFF&} forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayakashi reside in a host,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and humans reside in the physical plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:18:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Mononoke is formed with an Ayakashi as its host,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fed by the fates of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, when a Mononoke comes into the human plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it must be{\alpha&HFF} killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it must be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Ghost Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will{\alpha&HFF&} cleanse this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will cleanse{\alpha&HFF&} this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will cleanse this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mononoke must be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d like to embark on the second stage as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.02,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s unlike me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, Ichikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men are born into this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayakashi simply come into being.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If birth and being are accompanied by Truth and Regret,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they gain a Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they gain a Form, they become a\NMononoke, which should not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot eradicate the Mononoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we can purify them, and put them to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:22:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, there must be a sword,\Nand hands in which it might rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends, let me ask you of your Truth and Regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.13,0:22:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as Mononoke roam{\alpha&HFF&} this world…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as Mononoke roam this world…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m coming!
